  <brief_title>A Phase IIb Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Tolerability of Lower Doses Cinaciguat (25 µg/h, 10 µg/h) Given Intravenously to Patients With Acute Decompensated Chronic Congestive Heart Failure (ADHF)</brief_title>
  <acronym>COMPOSE 2</acronym>
  <official_title>A Placebo Controlled, Randomized, Double-Blind, Fixed-dose, Multicenter, Phase IIb Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Tolerability of Low Dose BAY58-2667 (25 µg/h, 10 µg/h) Given Intravenously to Subjects With Acute Decompensated Chronic Congestive Heart Failure (ADHF)</official_title>
